Tigoni was the genesis of the Lari massacre – and there are many more such mistakes that only require an open apology. The church can lead from the front, now that they know what their forefathers did. The man at the centre of the Nairobi-Tripoli alliance was the late Alex Muriithi, who also called himself Alex Kibaki. Nanyuki, before the railway, was turning into a lawless jungle. The former Nairobi governor also explains why he did not file an election petition. The university student is now the prime suspect in the multiple homicides his parents, brother, cousin and his father's worker. Tough-talking President Kenyatta tells off his critics, saying he is fully in charge of the country.